OL,3,CWill it become more expensive to cross
OL,4,Cthe Clifton Suspension Bridge?
OL,6,FIt could soon cost more to cross the
OL,7,FBristol Clifton Suspension Bridge as
OL,8,Fthe trust that runs the landmark is
OL,9,Flooking to put prices up.
OL,11,FThe Clifton Suspension Bridge Trust
OL,12,Fhas launched a public consultation on
OL,13,Fplans to raise the cost for cars and
OL,14,Fmotorcycles crossing the iconic
OL,15,FBristol landmark.
