OL,3,CWill it become more expensive to cross
OL,4,Cthe Clifton Suspension Bridge?
OL,6,FUnder proposed plans, the toll will
OL,7,Fincrease from #1 to #1.50 per crossing
OL,8,Fwith the trust saying it is having to
OL,9,Fhike prices because of increases in
OL,10,Finflation, maintenance costs and wage
OL,11,Fincreases.
OL,13,FThe change would come into effect in
OL,14,FJanuary 2027 but use of the bridge
OL,15,Fwill remain free of charge for
OL,16,Fpedestrians and cyclists.
OL,18,FThe proposals also include an annual
OL,19,Fincrease in the toll, because of
OL,20,Finflation, in the future.
