OL,3,CWill it become more expensive to cross
OL,4,Cthe Clifton Suspension Bridge?
OL,6,FThe Trust, which does not receive
OL,7,Fgovernment money to support upkeep or
OL,8,Foperation of the bridge, said the
OL,9,Fproposals were part of a strategy to
OL,10,Fprotect the landmark for future
OL,11,Fgenerations.
OL,13,FThe toll charge was last raised more
OL,14,Fthan a decade ago in 2014, from 50p to
OL,15,F#1.
OL,17,FThe consultation has already begun and
OL,18,Fwill close on 7 November.
